Package: Logolas
Type: Package
Title: Package for EDLogo visualization, featuring string logos and adaptive scaling of position weight matrices
Version: 1.2.1
Date: 10.10.2017.
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kushal", "Dey", email = "kkdey@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Dongyue", "Xie", email = "dyxie@uchicago.edu", role = c("ctb")),
    person("Matthew", "Stephens", email = "mstephens@uchicago.edu", role = c("ctb")))
Maintainer: Kushal Dey <kkdey@uchicago.edu>
Description: Produces logo plots highlighting both enrichment and depletion of characters called EDLogos, allows for plotting of string symbols, and performs scaling of position weights adaptively, along with several cool stylizations. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.3), ggplot2, gridBase
URL: https://github.com/kkdey/Logolas
